<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>72</hymn_number>
<author>China</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Belam No mawhpuopa en diu,
 A thihna ding tang zuonin a pui ui;
 A lungkhamna panpih a um puou maw,
 Gitloh puopa chu?

[V2]
 Aw, ka Lal a lieng, panpih ding nei loin,
 Kalvari tang zuonin a pui ui;
 Nu nauhaw chu lungkham tak in,
 Kap in chieh kit ui.

[V3]
 2. A thihna ding tang a tun tau.
 Bangtina a bawluh va en diu in;
 A put thinga etnawp din a khai ui,
 Mipin a nuihsan.

[V4]
 3. Ka et in ka nuihsan thei puoi,
 A thih dan chu thasiet a um ngei ie!
 A mai thiengtho thisan a dim zo tai,
 Aw hung en tiem u!

[V5]
 4. A thisan hung luonna zalin,
 Thiemloh chang, gitloha albang vaite;
 Hinna lampi ding chu a hun hawng tai,
 A chate hawh din.</lyrics>
<title>Ka Lal liengvai</title>
</song>